<chapter id="Chapter574636">
   <title>Customer Relationship Management (CRM) Module</title>
   <para>This module enables you to effectively organize
  Customer, Vendor, and other relationships in a centralized fashion. The
  system gives you the ability to store Addresses in a unified Address Book.
  It also enables you to track Incidents and To-Do's in a system-wide
  environment. The following topics will be covered in this chapter:</para>
